              </li>
              <li>
                Agility jumping
                <strong>obstacles tipping/falling</strong>
                to capture the chaotic fun of a dog “crashing” a jump.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='case-study-wrapper'>
